---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";

import ProjectHeader from "../../components/ProjectHeader.astro";
import SmallHeading from "../../components/SmallHeading.astro";
import ProjectGrid6Cols from "../../components/ProjectGrid6Cols.astro";
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import Caption from "../../components/Caption.astro";

import HeaderImage from "../../images/homepage/greenways.png";
import OldHomepage from "../../images/greenways/old-homepage.png";

import OldSiteMap from "../../images/greenways/old-sitemap.png";
import NewSiteMap from "../../images/greenways/new-sitemap.png";

import greenwaysHome from "../../images/greenways/greenways-homescreen.png";
import greenwaysRec from "../../images/greenways/greenways-rec.webm";
import greenwaysRecMp4 from "../../images/greenways/greenways-rec.mp4";

import Homepage2 from "../../images/greenways/Homepage-2.png";
import HomepageChuck from "../../images/greenways/homepage-chuck.png";
import offerings from "../../images/greenways/offerings.png";

import mobile from "../../images/greenways/greenways-mobile.webm";
import mobileMp4 from "../../images/greenways/greenways-mobile.mp4";

import project1 from "../../images/greenways/project-1.png";
import project2 from "../../images/greenways/project-2.png";
import project3 from "../../images/greenways/project-3.png";
import project4 from "../../images/greenways/project-4.png";
import project5 from "../../images/greenways/project-5.png";

---

<Layout title="Brian Sekelsky">
  <main>

    <ProjectHeader
      title="Greenways.com"
      objective="Elizabeth and I (as Best Parts) were hired by Chuck Flink to re-design his website, Greenways.com. Chuck Flink is an accomplished landscape architect and greenways consultant. He wanted a new website to catalog his work over the years and serve as a hub for new clients and collaborators to find him."
      types={[
        "Web Design",
        "Wordpress Development",
        "Branding"
      ]}
      collaborators={[
        "Elizabeth Gabriel",
      ]}
      year="2025"
      outboundLink="https://greenways.com"
      myColor="honeydew"
    />
    <div class="border-b load-in relative">
      <video class="w-full" playsinline autoplay muted loop>
        <source src={greenwaysRec} type="video/webm" />
        <source src={greenwaysRecMp4} type="video/mp4" />
      </video>
    </div>
    <ProjectGrid6Cols>
  <div class="col-span-2">
    <SmallHeading text="Organization and content management" />
    <p>
      We built Chuck’s site on WordPress so he can update content himself. A self-service CMS ensures he won’t need developer support just to add a new project or tweak copy.
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="col-span-4">
    <Image
      src={HeaderImage}
      alt="WordPress-powered homepage for Greenways.com"
      class="rounded-md shadow"
    />
    <Caption text="Homepage built on top of Wordpress" />
  </div>

  <div class="col-span-2">
    <SmallHeading text="Sitemap overhaul" />
    <p>
      The old structure was deep and confusing. We flattened the hierarchy around Chuck’s core services, making it easier for visitors to find what they need in one click.
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="col-span-2 flex flex-col justify-between">
    <Image
      src={OldSiteMap}
      alt="Diagram showing the original Greenways.com sitemap"
      class="rounded-md"
    />
    <Caption text="Original sitemap" />
  </div>
  <div class="col-span-2 flex flex-col justify-between">
    <Image
      src={NewSiteMap}
      alt="Diagram showing the revised Greenways.com sitemap"
      class="rounded-md"
    />
    <Caption text="Revised sitemap" />
  </div>

  <div class="col-span-2">
    <SmallHeading text="Visual refresh" />
    <p>
      Chuck’s brand needed a modern, clean aesthetic that still felt rooted in nature. We introduced a light palette, clear typography, and generous white space to foreground his portfolio.
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="col-span-4 grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
    <div class="flex flex-col justify-between">
      <Image
        src={OldHomepage}
        alt="Screenshot of Greenways.com before the redesign"
        class="rounded-md"
      />
      <Caption text="Before" />
    </div>
    <div class="flex flex-col justify-between">
      <Image
        src={HeaderImage}
        alt="Screenshot of Greenways.com after the redesign"
        class="rounded-md"
      />
      <Caption text="After" />
    </div>
  </div>
<div class="col-span-2">
    <SmallHeading text="Custom project illustrations" />
    <p>
      Elizabeth created a bespoke botanical illustration for each of Chuck’s five highlighted projects.  
      Each drawing features a plant native to its region, grounding the site in real landscapes and adding a layer of local storytelling.
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="col-span-4 grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
    <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
      <Image
        src={project1}
        alt="Botanical illustration for project one"
        class="rounded-md shadow"
      />
    </div>
    <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
      <Image
        src={project2}
        alt="Botanical illustration for project two"
        class="rounded-md shadow"
      />
    </div>
    <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
      <Image
        src={project3}
        alt="Botanical illustration for project three"
        class="rounded-md shadow"
      />
    </div>
    <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
      <Image
        src={project4}
        alt="Botanical illustration for project four"
        class="rounded-md shadow"
      />
    </div>
    <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
      <Image
        src={project5}
        alt="Botanical illustration for project five"
        class="rounded-md shadow"
      />
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="col-span-2">
    <SmallHeading text="Highlighting expertise" />
    <p>
      We carved out a dedicated intro section on the homepage to spotlight Chuck’s credentials and past projects.
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="col-span-4">
    <Image
      src={HomepageChuck}
      alt="Homepage section introducing Chuck Flink"
      class="rounded-md shadow"
    />
    <Caption text="Feature: Expert profile" />
  </div>

  <div class="col-span-2">
    <SmallHeading text="Clarifying offerings" />
    <p>
      Chuck’s services can seem specialized at first glance. We created a scannable offerings grid that breaks down each service into plain-language headings and short descriptions.
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="col-span-4">
    <Image
      src={offerings}
      alt="Offerings section showing services categories"
      class="rounded-md shadow"
    />
    <Caption text="Interactive service breakdown" />
  </div>

  <div class="col-span-2">
    <SmallHeading text="Responsiveness" />
    <p>
      The legacy site was desktop-only. We rebuilt every component to adapt fluidly from desktop to tablet and mobile, this ensures touch targets, layout, and typography scale seamlessly.
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="col-span-4">
    <div class="flex justify-center">
      <video playsinline autoplay muted loop class="rounded-md shadow">
        <source src={mobile} type="video/webm" />
        <source src={mobileMp4} type="video/mp4" />
      </video>
    </div>
    <Caption text="Mobile view" />
  </div>

  <div class="col-span-2">
    <SmallHeading text="Final reflection" />
    <p>
      Chuck Flink's new website is an organized repository for all of his professional achievements. New clients are able to quickly get in contact with him and find important information about him with ease.
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="col-span-4">
    <video playsinline autoplay muted loop>
      <source src={greenwaysRec} type="video/webm" />
      <source src={greenwaysRecMp4} type="video/mp4" />
    </video>
    <Caption text="Live site view" />
  </div>
</ProjectGrid6Cols>
  </main>
</Layout>